WEBVTT

00:07.560 --> 00:08.960
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:37.120 --> 01:42.800
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

01:47.400 --> 01:50.320
Firecrackers should herald
the Chinese New Year.

01:51.600 --> 01:53.320
Yet, while the summer heat lingers,

01:54.040 --> 01:55.520
the air is already thick
with the festive spirit.

01:55.600 --> 01:57.960
The blasting has lasted
from the Mao hour to the Shen hour.

01:58.640 --> 01:59.560
Everyone's saying

01:59.640 --> 02:02.160
the frontier troops nearly tore apart
the Northern Desert King's tent.

02:02.240 --> 02:04.880
Mr. Xie,
do you still intend to go to the frontier?

02:05.480 --> 02:08.160
The Northern Desert King
is already at the end of his rope.

02:09.479 --> 02:12.760
Why should I get entangled in this mess?

02:15.360 --> 02:18.280
I'll just send some nobody
to go through the motions.

02:18.800 --> 02:20.440
This was supposed to be our setup.

02:21.280 --> 02:23.200
Had it not been for Xie Yanlai,
Zhong Changrong would be dead.

02:23.800 --> 02:26.240
Once your men in Wangcheng
killed the Northern Desert King

02:26.320 --> 02:27.840
and Liang Qiang moved in
to reclaim Wangcheng,

02:27.920 --> 02:30.360
the frontier troops would be ours
for the taking.

02:31.720 --> 02:34.480
That brat's meddling
ruined the entire plan.

02:35.880 --> 02:37.040
What's the rush?

02:38.320 --> 02:41.400
The merit roll still lists
a Xie at the top.

02:42.960 --> 02:45.680
Does it really matter
who leads the troops?

02:47.560 --> 02:52.160
Besides, it's not even certain
he'll live to collect his reward.

02:52.880 --> 02:54.080
Mr. Xie, you mean…?

02:57.680 --> 02:59.480
The moonlight is stunning.

03:00.160 --> 03:02.200
Let's put the celebration banquet aside.

03:03.160 --> 03:06.600
I must first give Mr. Deng
a proper send-off.

03:07.320 --> 03:11.360
CHARTING THE COSMOS

03:16.440 --> 03:17.720
Something's on fire.

03:18.880 --> 03:19.720
Not quite.

03:20.320 --> 03:23.480
I've been around enough forest fires
to smell one before it starts.

03:30.960 --> 03:32.120
‎WRITE FOR ETERNITY

03:43.680 --> 03:45.400
The fire spread fast and fierce.

03:46.280 --> 03:48.800
They've drenched the room in fire oil.

03:49.520 --> 03:52.120
Had I been a moment later,
I would not have made it out.

03:54.600 --> 03:55.480
Deng Yi died

03:57.920 --> 03:59.240
just like that?

04:00.920 --> 04:02.520
<i>I don't usually get along with Mr. Deng.</i>

04:03.320 --> 04:07.160
But I refuse to believe
he would collude with our enemies.

04:07.240 --> 04:11.360
For the moment, our priority
is to stabilize the court.

04:12.280 --> 04:13.440
Mr. Deng has been confined.

04:14.040 --> 04:17.320
At this moment, I should step up.

04:18.399 --> 04:20.240
"To stabilize the court"?

04:22.079 --> 04:23.760
"Step up"? How noble.

04:24.280 --> 04:26.360
Xie Yanfang truly is a master of strategy.

04:27.040 --> 04:28.160
Everything is flawlessly calculated.

04:28.760 --> 04:31.920
The Imperial Guard Office
is still investigating the fire,

04:32.440 --> 04:34.800
and the body has been sent to the coroner.

04:41.400 --> 04:44.280
Your Highness. Your Highness!

04:44.960 --> 04:51.200
XIE RESIDENCE

05:02.480 --> 05:04.400
Your Highness, I suppose
you heard about Mr. Deng…

05:04.480 --> 05:06.080
Did you order his death?

05:07.880 --> 05:09.320
Your Highness, what is this about?

05:09.920 --> 05:12.280
Who else would dare?

05:15.920 --> 05:17.680
Your Highness, you are mistaken.

05:18.920 --> 05:19.880
There is another

05:21.800 --> 05:23.520
who has the nerve,

05:25.040 --> 05:26.120
the will,

05:26.960 --> 05:29.480
and far more reason besides.

05:34.720 --> 05:36.120
And that person is you,

05:37.560 --> 05:39.120
the Grand Princess.

05:39.920 --> 05:42.240
You and Mr. Deng have long been at odds.

05:42.320 --> 05:44.400
The Grand Mentor's Residence
is filled with the Imperial Guards.

05:44.480 --> 05:49.760
How could suspicion
for his murder ever fall on me?

05:50.440 --> 05:51.880
If I were to kill him,

05:52.480 --> 05:56.400
it would be according to the law,
with clear evidence, and for all to see.

05:57.680 --> 05:59.080
Is Your Highness suggesting

06:01.560 --> 06:04.320
I am underhanded

06:06.480 --> 06:09.120
and can only operate in the shadows?

06:10.200 --> 06:12.160
Even if I killed him,

06:13.720 --> 06:18.240
would you really kill me for revenge?

06:19.520 --> 06:23.760
Are you using this opportunity
to get rid of me as well?

06:33.960 --> 06:38.240
I never thought
that you would be the one to save me.

06:39.480 --> 06:42.480
Mr. Deng, did you really think
a lock could keep me

06:43.000 --> 06:44.400
in that side residence?

06:45.720 --> 06:48.320
I was merely waiting
for the perfect moment

06:48.840 --> 06:50.560
to leave the Capital.

06:52.200 --> 06:55.880
I never imagined that beneath the city
lay such a secret.

06:56.600 --> 06:57.960
In your eyes,

06:59.080 --> 07:03.240
the Capital is just a board
for power struggles.

07:05.200 --> 07:09.800
Father, however, viewed it
as a home to return to.

07:10.600 --> 07:11.720
Over the years,

07:12.920 --> 07:15.520
he remembered everything,

07:17.160 --> 07:21.200
from the halls of noble mansions
to the very number of bluestone slabs

07:21.280 --> 07:22.960
on these streets.

07:25.240 --> 07:26.240
Indeed.

07:27.360 --> 07:28.640
No threshold in the imperial city,

07:29.440 --> 07:32.960
however high, can keep out
those who yearn for home.

07:34.360 --> 07:35.680
I suppose

07:36.280 --> 07:39.160
I am nothing more
than His Lordship's gatekeeper,

07:39.760 --> 07:42.320
entrusted with his
most precious holding of all,

07:42.960 --> 07:43.800
this Capital.

07:44.600 --> 07:45.640
It's all fated.

07:46.800 --> 07:51.280
It was written
that I would save you tonight.

07:55.040 --> 07:57.240
Mr. Deng, your meal is ready.

08:02.040 --> 08:03.560
They have come for you.

08:04.360 --> 08:05.680
Were it not for me,

08:07.200 --> 08:10.880
this is where your life ends.

08:12.440 --> 08:15.200
Tie Ying, set the fire. Let's go.

08:21.640 --> 08:23.360
With this water,

08:24.600 --> 08:28.640
let's toast to our escape

08:30.480 --> 08:31.920
from the jaws of death.

08:42.440 --> 08:46.120
Was it Her Highness
who wanted to kill you?

08:47.000 --> 08:48.160
It was not her.

08:49.920 --> 08:50.840
It was Xie Yanfang.

08:53.560 --> 08:55.640
To think he could be so vicious.

08:57.400 --> 08:58.680
I favor poison.

08:59.680 --> 09:01.200
Yet he proved even more venomous.

09:05.000 --> 09:07.280
Thank you for saving my life,
Your Highness.

09:07.360 --> 09:08.960
What is it you desire, Your Highness?

09:10.920 --> 09:12.120
Speak plainly.

09:13.400 --> 09:14.640
I've bided my time in the depths
long enough.

09:16.760 --> 09:19.280
Mr. Deng, since you're always cautious,

09:20.160 --> 09:23.440
I assume everything that matters
is close at hand.

09:27.080 --> 09:29.720
Please, Mr. Deng, escort me home.

09:37.360 --> 09:38.920
Can we actually get away?

09:42.920 --> 09:45.960
I have arranged
for someone to die in your place.

09:49.360 --> 09:50.840
That should buy us some time.

10:03.240 --> 10:06.640
Your Highness, Zhu Yong just reported
that the corpse was not Mr. Deng.

10:07.520 --> 10:08.440
What?

10:09.360 --> 10:11.360
-Are you certain?
-The coroner has finished the examination.

10:11.440 --> 10:12.560
It is confirmed.

11:17.320 --> 11:18.680
The dew feels chilly.

11:33.040 --> 11:34.760
Your Highness is too precious to fall ill.

11:37.160 --> 11:38.320
Please take care.

11:59.680 --> 12:01.560
It has come to this after all.

12:02.080 --> 12:03.880
With Xie Yanlai's great merit,

12:04.920 --> 12:06.880
the frontier troops under the Xie Family,

12:06.960 --> 12:11.880
and no footing whatsoever
left for you in Xiao Yu's court,

12:12.600 --> 12:14.560
why suffer under Chu Zhao and Xie Yanfang

12:15.520 --> 12:16.880
when you could come with me
to Xiaonan Prefecture?

12:18.360 --> 12:19.760
If I ascend to the throne,

12:20.680 --> 12:22.880
you will still be the Grand Mentor
of the State of Chu.

12:53.760 --> 12:55.240
He is indeed not Deng Yi.

12:56.200 --> 12:57.600
Good thing we retrieved the body in time.

12:58.200 --> 12:59.800
If the face had been burned
beyond recognition,

12:59.880 --> 13:01.240
it would be impossible to identify.

13:01.320 --> 13:03.320
I fear that should something happen
to Mr. Deng,

13:03.400 --> 13:05.160
regardless of whether he lives,
it will be detrimental to Your Highness.

13:05.800 --> 13:07.720
Someone will frame you
for wanting him eliminated.

13:08.720 --> 13:09.760
What does this have to do
with Her Highness?

13:09.840 --> 13:11.160
All the officials saw

13:11.240 --> 13:14.880
the Imperial Guard Office
escort him to the imperial city

13:14.960 --> 13:15.920
and lock him in his residence.

13:16.000 --> 13:17.920
Now that the frontier troops
have captured the Northern Desert King,

13:18.000 --> 13:19.840
Your Highness's influence is surging.

13:19.920 --> 13:23.000
Eliminating him now would not stir unrest.

13:23.080 --> 13:24.120
The timing could not be better.

13:24.800 --> 13:25.800
That is nonsense.

13:26.400 --> 13:28.040
Her Highness has no reason
to kill Mr. Deng.

13:28.120 --> 13:30.720
Disagreement in policy
and struggle for power

13:30.800 --> 13:32.400
are reason enough.

13:34.320 --> 13:38.240
If Xiaoman had not been fast enough
to charge into the fire and drag him out,

13:38.840 --> 13:42.440
we would truly believe he was dead.

13:43.800 --> 13:46.160
The first problem we must resolve

13:46.240 --> 13:48.120
is those issues
you're worried about, Mr. Zhu.

13:48.200 --> 13:50.560
So this body is a stand-in?

13:51.600 --> 13:53.800
Did he arrange this himself,
or was it someone else's doing?

13:54.320 --> 13:55.440
And what was the purpose?

13:56.960 --> 13:58.160
To fake his death and escape?

13:58.680 --> 13:59.720
Xiao Xun.

14:00.720 --> 14:01.560
Zhu Yong,

14:01.640 --> 14:03.440
go to Xiao Xun's residence immediately
and report back what you find.

14:03.520 --> 14:04.200
Yes.

14:12.520 --> 14:17.760
WRITE FOR ETERNITY

14:17.840 --> 14:19.720
The entire Grand Mentor's Residence
has been searched,

14:19.800 --> 14:21.480
but there is no trace of Deng Yi.

14:21.560 --> 14:23.960
We kept watch outside,
and not a soul was seen coming or going.

14:24.480 --> 14:27.320
But there must be something we missed.

14:28.040 --> 14:29.920
He couldn't just vanish into thin air.

14:31.080 --> 14:33.160
They knew you were posted outside.

14:33.240 --> 14:36.440
They wouldn't have moved
without a way out.

14:38.720 --> 14:40.720
By the way,
is Mr. Deng's mother still here?

14:41.360 --> 14:44.080
Everyone in the Grand Mentor's Residence
is under guard.

14:44.160 --> 14:46.080
Mr. Deng's mother
has been placed under separate care.

14:56.440 --> 14:59.800
We searched where Mr. Deng
conducts his affairs too.

15:01.000 --> 15:02.040
The Imperial Seal alone is missing.

15:06.000 --> 15:07.200
That was my oversight.

15:08.520 --> 15:09.840
It is not your fault, Your Highness.

15:10.600 --> 15:13.480
Mr. Deng was under confinement
and yet to be convicted.

15:14.800 --> 15:16.800
No one has the authority to seize

15:16.880 --> 15:18.360
the Imperial Seal gifted
by the late Emperor.

15:19.000 --> 15:21.120
Mr. Deng's power and influence

15:21.200 --> 15:23.000
stemmed from the position
granted by the late Emperor

15:23.080 --> 15:24.480
and his possession of the Imperial Seal.

15:25.120 --> 15:27.520
Whether he faked his death
or was taken away,

15:27.600 --> 15:29.160
he would surely take it with him.

15:32.440 --> 15:34.760
Your Highness, Xiao Xun is gone indeed.

15:36.800 --> 15:37.640
Relay my order.

15:37.720 --> 15:38.880
Lock down all city gates immediately.

15:40.280 --> 15:42.000
Your Highness, there is
a secret passage in the room.

15:56.320 --> 16:01.440
Deng Yi and Xiao Xun
have finally joined forces.

16:02.200 --> 16:07.000
Once they return to Xiaonan Prefecture,
they will seize the chance to rebel.

16:13.280 --> 16:17.400
Is the course of fate
truly beyond my reach,

16:19.200 --> 16:21.080
no matter how hard I struggle?

16:30.760 --> 16:31.640
Mr. Xie,

16:34.880 --> 16:37.560
we used poison,
so why did a fire break out?

16:38.200 --> 16:40.240
A minor mishap from an unexpected twist,

16:41.320 --> 16:43.000
but of no consequence.

16:43.600 --> 16:45.760
Du Qi, get things ready.

16:45.840 --> 16:46.680
I need to make a long journey.

16:47.560 --> 16:48.600
Where to?

16:49.120 --> 16:52.760
North of the Cang River, to intercept
the Lord of Xiaonan's rebel forces.

16:56.160 --> 16:57.520
Since when did they rebel?

17:00.240 --> 17:04.480
Our grand mentor is soon to become theirs.

17:06.839 --> 17:07.880
Only then

17:09.040 --> 17:12.720
will he and Her Highness be truly locked
in a fight to the death.

17:14.640 --> 17:16.319
This is more intriguing

17:18.520 --> 17:19.800
than my original plan.

17:23.200 --> 17:24.440
‎XIAONAN

17:24.520 --> 17:28.200
-Wish Your Lordship a long life.
-Wish Your Lordship a long life.

17:39.720 --> 17:41.720
Your Lordship,
His Majesty's gift has arrived.

17:42.720 --> 17:44.880
I'm glad he thinks of me.

17:44.960 --> 17:45.880
That is enough.

17:47.000 --> 17:48.600
Nothing warms my heart more

17:48.680 --> 17:50.920
than the people of Xiaonan
celebrating in the streets

17:51.000 --> 17:52.400
of their own accord.

17:53.000 --> 17:53.880
Indeed.

17:53.960 --> 17:57.840
Distribute these among the people,
so they may share in the joy.

17:58.440 --> 18:00.280
Your Lordship, you seem to have forgotten

18:00.360 --> 18:03.560
His Highness's gift
arrived alongside His Majesty's.

18:04.400 --> 18:05.360
Yes.

18:05.440 --> 18:06.600
Bring it forward.

18:06.680 --> 18:09.760
Let me see what surprise he has for me.

18:13.160 --> 18:14.960
‎LONGEVITY

18:18.280 --> 18:20.000
‎LONGEVITY

18:20.080 --> 18:23.040
Each character is written
by His Highness himself.

18:23.120 --> 18:23.960
Your Lordship,

18:24.040 --> 18:26.400
this is the Scroll of Longevity
from His Highness.

18:26.480 --> 18:30.040
Such devotion is truly quite impressive!

18:32.520 --> 18:34.120
Come. Everyone, take a look.

18:41.360 --> 18:42.920
Xun must have put in a lot of effort.

18:43.000 --> 18:44.680
Writing in such small script

18:44.760 --> 18:47.080
-must have strained his eyes.
-Indeed.

18:47.800 --> 18:50.240
Each character is written
in a different style.

18:50.320 --> 18:52.040
Xun is truly thoughtful.

18:54.920 --> 18:56.640
The scent of the ink
is quite unique as well.

18:56.720 --> 18:58.880
His Highness has arrived!

18:58.960 --> 19:01.080
Father! Father!

19:01.160 --> 19:05.280
-Xun, are you the true surprise?
-Father, quick.

19:05.360 --> 19:06.200
Throw it away! It is poisoned!

19:06.280 --> 19:07.280
Father.

19:08.760 --> 19:10.120
Your Highness, what are you…?

19:12.960 --> 19:13.920
Father.

19:15.760 --> 19:17.520
-Father.
-Your Lordship.

19:18.560 --> 19:19.400
Your Lordship!

19:19.480 --> 19:21.160
-Father.
-Your Lordship.

19:21.240 --> 19:22.680
-Your Lordship.
-Your Lordship.

19:23.200 --> 19:24.680
Father.

19:26.760 --> 19:28.880
Father. Father!

19:28.960 --> 19:31.320
FOREVER GRATEFUL FOR HEAVEN’S GRACE

19:35.640 --> 19:36.920
-Your Lordship!
-Father!

19:38.320 --> 19:39.440
Father!

19:40.920 --> 19:43.640
Your Highness, what is going on?

19:43.720 --> 19:45.320
Why has His Lordship been poisoned?

19:51.840 --> 19:52.880
The poison lies within the script.

19:53.920 --> 19:55.680
Once inhaled, it pierces the vitals.

19:58.520 --> 19:59.840
Father.

20:01.520 --> 20:03.360
Sir, quick. Check on His Lordship.

20:08.520 --> 20:11.440
But Your Highness,
you prepared this yourself.

20:11.520 --> 20:13.200
How could it be poisoned?

20:13.800 --> 20:14.920
When the palace said

20:15.560 --> 20:18.240
they would present the gifts
to Father on my behalf,

20:18.880 --> 20:19.920
I gave it little thought.

20:20.600 --> 20:24.400
Once I finished the Scroll of Longevity,
I handed it over to the palace.

20:25.120 --> 20:27.920
But several days ago, someone told me

20:30.040 --> 20:33.840
that my gift
might cost my father his life.

20:33.920 --> 20:38.000
He said the scroll
had been soaked in poison.

20:39.280 --> 20:41.840
I knew Father would pay no mind
to gifts from the court,

20:42.600 --> 20:45.680
yet would examine
anything from me with great care.

20:45.760 --> 20:49.080
Close enough to inspect it,
he would inhale the poison from the ink,

20:49.640 --> 20:50.480
and…

20:51.080 --> 20:53.040
He helped me flee the Capital.

20:53.120 --> 20:56.320
I traveled day and night to stop Father,

20:56.920 --> 21:00.520
but I was still a step too late.

21:00.600 --> 21:02.320
-Father!
-Your Highness. Your Highness,

21:02.400 --> 21:03.920
you must remain calm.

21:04.640 --> 21:06.320
Is there any way to save His Lordship?

21:13.960 --> 21:16.120
Mr. Deng, please, save my Father!

21:16.720 --> 21:18.920
Deng Yi? Why are you here?

21:19.000 --> 21:21.360
-Guards, seize him.
-You have it all wrong.

21:22.240 --> 21:24.040
It was Mr. Deng who helped me return.

21:24.840 --> 21:27.840
Your Highness, the person
you mentioned earlier was him?

21:32.400 --> 21:33.320
Mr. Deng.

21:34.960 --> 21:35.920
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

21:36.000 --> 21:38.120
Please save my father.

21:38.200 --> 21:39.560
I beg of you.

21:40.400 --> 21:42.440
Well… Mr. Deng,

21:43.160 --> 21:45.040
please, save His Lordship.

21:45.120 --> 21:47.160
-Mr. Deng, save His Lordship.
-Please.

21:47.240 --> 21:48.680
I implore you, Mr. Deng.

21:52.000 --> 21:53.160
Your Highness, please rise.

21:56.080 --> 21:59.800
I do as you wish,
but you must keep your promise.

22:09.880 --> 22:10.920
Mr. Deng.

22:11.680 --> 22:13.120
The poison runs too deep.

22:14.320 --> 22:15.160
He is beyond saving.

22:16.520 --> 22:17.720
Father!

22:17.800 --> 22:18.920
Your Highness.

22:19.440 --> 22:20.400
Father.

22:20.920 --> 22:22.400
-Since you told His Highness
-Father.

22:22.480 --> 22:25.440
about the poison and helped him escape,

22:25.520 --> 22:27.680
-you must know something.
-Indeed.

22:27.760 --> 22:30.000
His Lordship has sent His Highness
to the Capital as a hostage,

22:30.080 --> 22:33.360
so who would want to harm His Lordship?

22:33.440 --> 22:35.440
Mr. Deng, who exactly is behind this?

22:38.080 --> 22:38.920
The late Emperor.

22:39.920 --> 22:41.320
What? The late Emperor?

22:41.400 --> 22:42.440
How is that possible?

22:42.520 --> 22:43.720
Mr. Deng, you must be mistaken.

22:43.800 --> 22:45.560
If the late Emperor
wanted His Lordship dead,

22:45.640 --> 22:47.560
why wait until now?

22:48.280 --> 22:49.440
I mean,

22:50.360 --> 22:54.600
it was the late Emperor who sowed
the seeds of His Lordship's end.

22:55.600 --> 22:58.960
Do you know
who the late Emperor designated

22:59.480 --> 23:04.200
as the Crown Prince on his deathbed
when the Capital was in peril?

23:04.920 --> 23:05.920
His grandson, wasn't it?

23:06.520 --> 23:07.560
-Yes.
-No.

23:09.200 --> 23:10.800
It was the heir to the Lord of Xiaonan,

23:12.160 --> 23:13.480
-Xiao Xun.
-What?

23:14.360 --> 23:16.360
Is this true? How can we trust you?

23:22.640 --> 23:24.040
"Xiao Xun, heir to the Lord of Xiaonan,

23:24.760 --> 23:28.600
is virtuous, wise,
beneficent to the people,

23:28.680 --> 23:30.720
and judicious in governance.

23:30.800 --> 23:34.680
He shall ascend the imperial throne
and bear the weight of the state."

23:36.640 --> 23:40.240
On his deathbed,
the late Emperor named Xiao Xun

23:40.840 --> 23:42.400
as his heir.

23:45.000 --> 23:48.440
The late Emperor did issue
this decree on his deathbed.

23:49.080 --> 23:51.000
I am the witness.

23:52.240 --> 23:54.600
However, Chu Zhao
and the Xie Family conspired

23:54.680 --> 23:57.520
to hold the late Emperor hostage
and forced him to issue a new decree.

23:58.960 --> 23:59.960
This imperial edict

24:01.200 --> 24:04.280
never even made it past the palace gates.

24:22.360 --> 24:25.200
XIAONAN

24:53.160 --> 24:54.160
Father,

24:56.120 --> 24:57.560
are you unable to sleep,

24:58.720 --> 25:00.240
or is sleep simply beyond your reach?

25:04.800 --> 25:05.720
Do not fear.

25:07.240 --> 25:09.320
Soon, you will be able to rest soundly,

25:10.560 --> 25:11.920
never to wake again.

25:16.560 --> 25:19.840
You always loved
to stroke my face like this,

25:21.800 --> 25:25.360
and I always loved
lingering close beside you.

25:26.920 --> 25:28.120
Among all your children,

25:29.320 --> 25:33.560
only I was blessed with such affection.

25:34.640 --> 25:36.880
To repay your indulgence,

25:37.480 --> 25:41.160
now that I've sat on the throne,

25:42.520 --> 25:44.000
I shall honor you as the late Emperor.

25:45.200 --> 25:47.240
At last, your wish is fulfilled.

25:49.800 --> 25:50.840
Father.

25:52.360 --> 25:53.320
Are you happy?

25:57.400 --> 25:58.600
I am truly happy.

26:01.000 --> 26:05.120
Although I used to say
I wanted to help you fulfill your wishes,

26:05.800 --> 26:08.520
I never knew if I would feel happy

26:09.960 --> 26:11.680
once they were accomplished.

26:12.600 --> 26:14.200
But now I understand.

26:15.400 --> 26:18.840
So this is what it feels like
to be happy for oneself.

26:28.200 --> 26:29.720
It's finally done.

26:30.560 --> 26:32.760
I should go visit Mr. Deng.

26:33.640 --> 26:37.280
Tie Ying, bring the Golden Finch Venom
and soak the scroll.

26:49.080 --> 26:53.320
Mr. Deng, what brings you here?

26:54.000 --> 26:55.320
The decree has reached

26:55.400 --> 26:58.040
Xiaonan Prefecture
and the eight commanderies

26:58.120 --> 26:59.200
and 12 cities beyond.

26:59.280 --> 27:01.800
Outside the prefecture,
30,000 regional troops

27:01.880 --> 27:04.480
have lifted their defenses
and stand ready to be commanded.

27:05.120 --> 27:06.240
I appreciate it, Mr. Deng.

27:08.040 --> 27:11.400
The Prince of State's Residence
is stronger than ever

27:11.920 --> 27:14.160
with you on our side.

27:15.080 --> 27:16.200
Your Highness is too kind.

27:16.920 --> 27:18.760
It is His Lordship's foresight
we should credit.

27:19.280 --> 27:21.320
All those decades of winning loyalty,

27:21.960 --> 27:24.720
and one command is all it would take.

27:28.280 --> 27:29.760
Yet no command ever came.

27:30.360 --> 27:33.960
Father held it back for decades.

27:34.800 --> 27:36.280
Without you,

27:36.960 --> 27:39.360
today would have been no different.

27:40.520 --> 27:46.040
It seems His Lordship
owes Your Highness thanks.

27:47.080 --> 27:48.640
You willingly threw away

27:48.720 --> 27:53.640
His Lordship's life
for control over the state.

27:57.440 --> 27:59.320
It was my father's wish.

28:01.560 --> 28:05.080
To see it fulfilled,
he cast me aside without hesitation.

28:05.720 --> 28:07.880
Much less would he spare himself.

28:09.120 --> 28:12.760
His death would be for a worthy cause.

28:13.560 --> 28:14.800
We have secured

28:15.320 --> 28:18.000
the garrison in Xiaonan
and the surrounding local forces.

28:18.720 --> 28:21.200
But progress toward the Capital
is far less smooth.

28:21.720 --> 28:23.240
The Grand Princess has reached out

28:23.320 --> 28:25.920
to all post houses
and prefectures along the route,

28:26.000 --> 28:28.320
and now, most of our decrees
have been intercepted.

28:33.200 --> 28:36.360
Who would have thought
the Grand Princess's decrees

28:37.120 --> 28:39.280
would carry more weight
than those of the Emperor?

28:41.960 --> 28:44.240
Your Majesty, everything is prepared.

28:44.920 --> 28:46.240
Please proceed
to the enthronement ceremony

28:46.320 --> 28:47.720
along with Mr. Deng.

29:07.360 --> 29:09.480
<i>The late Emperor's final decree is here.</i>

29:10.160 --> 29:11.600
<i>"In the autumn</i>
<i>of the 15th year of Tianshu,</i>

29:11.680 --> 29:13.400
I am approaching my end.

29:14.160 --> 29:15.920
Xiao Xun, heir to the Lord of Xiaonan,

29:16.000 --> 29:19.000
is virtuous, wise,
beneficent to the people,

29:19.080 --> 29:21.360
and judicious in governance.

29:21.440 --> 29:24.680
He shall ascend the imperial throne
and bear the weight of the state.

29:25.200 --> 29:29.080
Proclaim this to the world
so that all may know."

29:29.720 --> 29:30.880
Kneel.

29:32.880 --> 29:34.440
Kowtow.

29:36.040 --> 29:37.880
Rise.

29:39.320 --> 29:40.880
Kowtow.

29:44.600 --> 29:45.800
You may rise.

29:48.880 --> 29:50.280
Read the proclamation.

29:51.400 --> 29:53.000
"On the 27th day of the eighth month,

29:53.080 --> 29:54.480
in the third year of Xingping,

29:54.560 --> 29:56.360
the Prince of State passed away.

29:56.440 --> 29:58.680
Deng Yi, the Grand Mentor,
withdrew to Xiaonan Prefecture,

29:58.760 --> 30:00.680
carrying the late Emperor's final decree."

30:00.760 --> 30:03.360
<i>"No righteous men in court,</i>
<i>but traitors within.</i>

30:03.440 --> 30:06.960
<i>During the turmoil of the Yongning year,</i>
<i>the imperial in-law Xie Yanfang</i>

30:07.040 --> 30:09.800
<i>colluded with the frontier troops,</i>
<i>took the late Emperor hostage,</i>

30:10.320 --> 30:12.560
<i>usurped the throne,</i>
<i>bent the state to his will,</i>

30:12.640 --> 30:14.320
<i>and poisoned the Prince of State.</i>

30:15.040 --> 30:16.960
<i>In the ninth month</i>
<i>of the third year of Xingping,</i>

30:17.480 --> 30:20.760
<i>Xiao Xun, heir to the Prince of State,</i>
<i>acting on the late Emperor's decree,</i>

30:20.840 --> 30:22.440
<i>enthrones Chu Zhao as Empress,</i>

30:23.040 --> 30:25.000
<i>raises arms against</i>
<i>the treacherous Xie Yanfang</i>

30:25.080 --> 30:28.240
<i>to restore order,</i>
<i>and sets forth on campaign."</i>

30:34.440 --> 30:35.520
Move out.

30:42.840 --> 30:44.840
Deng Yi forged the imperial decree,

30:44.920 --> 30:47.840
claiming the late Emperor intended
to pass the throne to Xiao Xun.

30:48.520 --> 30:53.160
He holds the Imperial Seal,
so he can write whatever he pleases.

30:53.240 --> 30:54.880
The late Emperor was poisoned that night.

30:54.960 --> 30:57.200
Who knows what the truth really was?

30:59.200 --> 31:01.720
At this point, what is false becomes true.

31:01.800 --> 31:02.760
‎DILIGENT AND VIRTUOUS

31:02.840 --> 31:04.920
Ministers, do not be disturbed by rumors.

31:05.440 --> 31:07.760
Mr. Xie has blocked
the rebel army at the Cang River,

31:07.840 --> 31:09.760
and the Northern Desert King
has surrendered.

31:09.840 --> 31:11.480
The frontier will soon be stable.

31:11.560 --> 31:15.480
We have enough energy
and troops to quell the rebellion.

31:16.640 --> 31:18.720
Xiao Xun is merely walking
the same doomed path.

31:18.800 --> 31:21.240
Even with Deng Yi,
what could a pathetic wretch

31:21.760 --> 31:24.720
like him possibly amount to?

31:25.480 --> 31:29.280
His Majesty will issue the proclamation
and make it known to all.

31:30.640 --> 31:31.640
Court dismissed.

31:32.240 --> 31:34.920
-We bid farewell to Your Majesty
-We bid farewell to Your Majesty

31:35.000 --> 31:37.240
-and Your Highness.
-and Your Highness.

31:48.320 --> 31:51.640
You were so quick to grasp
"besieging Wei to rescue Zhao".

31:51.720 --> 31:52.840
Why are you struggling so much

31:52.920 --> 31:53.960
with "concealing the dagger
behind a smile"?

31:54.040 --> 31:57.560
Zhao, it's just so hard.

31:58.080 --> 32:00.080
Can I learn that some other time?

32:03.160 --> 32:05.560
Greetings, Your Majesty, Your Highness.

32:06.160 --> 32:07.400
‎I've come as decreed.

32:07.480 --> 32:08.600
Uncle, you're back.

32:13.240 --> 32:14.640
Mr. Xie, you must be exhausted.

32:14.720 --> 32:17.200
I thought you still had an hour to go.

32:17.280 --> 32:18.840
Fortunately, the meal is prepared.

32:18.920 --> 32:19.880
Please, take a seat and eat.

32:20.720 --> 32:21.640
I appreciate it.

32:21.720 --> 32:24.680
Uncle, try some and see
if it agrees with you.

32:34.040 --> 32:36.760
There's a new chef in the palace
who specializes in Gaoyang flavors.

32:37.360 --> 32:38.320
Yu finds it quite good.

32:38.400 --> 32:41.000
It tastes very much
like what his mother used to enjoy.

32:43.240 --> 32:44.320
It feels so good to be home.

32:49.240 --> 32:51.360
To see one's kin is to be home.

32:59.120 --> 33:02.200
The chef brewed this himself
with a traditional method.

33:02.280 --> 33:04.360
Yanfang, please, have a sip.

33:19.800 --> 33:20.640
Thank you.

33:20.720 --> 33:23.080
Uncle, try some of this.

33:23.160 --> 33:24.560
This is my favorite.

33:24.640 --> 33:25.520
Very well.

33:30.040 --> 33:31.000
Here, Yu.

33:34.760 --> 33:37.480
I have a chef who makes
exceptional rice cakes.

33:38.080 --> 33:40.800
I shall bring some
for Your Highness to try another day.

33:41.840 --> 33:43.720
Uncle, can I try some as well?

33:44.600 --> 33:45.440
Of course.

33:51.360 --> 33:52.400
Here.

33:52.480 --> 33:54.440
Uncle, try this.

34:00.480 --> 34:02.880
North of the Cang River,
three commanderies and 28 cities

34:03.640 --> 34:04.920
have all submitted to Xiao Xun.

34:05.720 --> 34:08.159
Together with the Lord of Xiaonan's
illegally raised forces,

34:09.320 --> 34:10.520
the total comes to 270,000.

34:11.400 --> 34:15.760
I never expected they could gather
so many troops in just a few months.

34:16.520 --> 34:21.199
Rebellions always begin
with a roar of momentum.

34:21.280 --> 34:24.760
Deng Yi stole the Tally
and the Imperial Seal.

34:25.360 --> 34:27.920
It is no surprise that many people
have been misled.

34:29.719 --> 34:33.120
In time, when the court
sends forces against them,

34:34.280 --> 34:35.480
people will see the truth.

34:37.960 --> 34:41.280
<i>Just like in the previous life,</i>
<i>Xiao Xun ascends to the throne,</i>

34:41.800 --> 34:43.880
<i>and the one who leads the campaign</i>
<i>against him is Xie Yanfang.</i>

34:51.120 --> 34:52.159
Do not worry.

34:53.120 --> 34:54.120
I am here.

34:56.480 --> 34:57.600
I am not worried.

34:58.360 --> 35:01.400
Once Jiu escorted the Northern Desert King
across the frontier,

35:02.000 --> 35:04.560
he could lead the troops
to provide support

35:04.640 --> 35:06.880
and form a pincer movement
with the court's forces.

35:06.960 --> 35:09.760
The Lord of Xiaonan's rebels
will be crushed.

35:12.880 --> 35:13.920
Do you miss him?

35:17.480 --> 35:18.320
What?

35:51.160 --> 35:52.200
The time has come.

35:52.840 --> 35:53.680
Let's go.

35:54.560 --> 35:58.960
Chu Ling must have wished to storm my tent

35:59.680 --> 36:01.320
just as you did.

36:01.920 --> 36:04.960
It is precisely because General Chu
kept you locked in battle for decades

36:05.760 --> 36:08.360
that I now have the chance
to take you down.

36:08.960 --> 36:10.240
You are very valorous.

36:11.760 --> 36:15.800
Your father must have been proud of you.

36:22.720 --> 36:24.720
My son is much stronger than you.

36:25.880 --> 36:29.640
He knew his father loved him
until the very end.

36:37.560 --> 36:38.880
I have one last question for you.

36:41.280 --> 36:44.960
What really happened
with that fire in the Wei Village

36:45.720 --> 36:47.320
five years ago?

36:52.760 --> 36:55.680
<i>Back then, Chu Ling allowed Alan Ruoying</i>

36:55.760 --> 36:59.000
<i>to fake her death and become</i>
<i>the bandit leader Mu Mianhong,</i>

36:59.080 --> 37:01.800
<i>who hid in the Cangmu Forest.</i>

37:01.880 --> 37:04.680
<i>So, we decided to make a deal</i>
<i>with the Lord of Xiaonan.</i>

37:04.760 --> 37:08.920
<i>We set a fire at the Wei Village</i>
<i>at the foot of the Cangmu Forest</i>

37:09.000 --> 37:12.280
<i>and left clues</i>
<i>to frame the Cangmu Stronghold.</i>

37:12.360 --> 37:15.320
<i>Once the court of the State of Chu</i>
<i>followed our lead</i>

37:15.400 --> 37:17.160
<i>to investigate the stronghold,</i>

37:17.680 --> 37:20.920
<i>they would discover</i>
<i>Mu Mianhong's true identity,</i>

37:21.600 --> 37:24.800
<i>which would serve</i>
<i>as ironclad proof of Chu Ling's treason.</i>

37:25.320 --> 37:28.040
<i>If Yunzhong Prefecture lost Chu Ling,</i>

37:28.120 --> 37:31.120
<i>seizing the frontier</i>
<i>would be a simple task.</i>

37:31.200 --> 37:33.320
<i>I do not know</i>

37:33.400 --> 37:36.000
<i>why the clues pointing</i>
<i>to the Cangmu Stronghold were erased</i>

37:36.080 --> 37:38.880
<i>and why you appeared in that fire</i>

37:39.720 --> 37:43.320
<i>and ended up taking the blame for us.</i>

37:44.080 --> 37:45.240
Later,

37:47.000 --> 37:49.400
I heard that the young man
from the Xie Family

37:49.480 --> 37:52.160
framed for burning the village
had gone to the frontier

37:52.240 --> 37:55.720
and become the most capable vanguard
by Chu Ling's side.

37:55.800 --> 38:00.520
As they say in the Central Plains,
the world never unfolds as planned.

38:01.760 --> 38:03.240
I never imagined

38:04.080 --> 38:06.960
we would meet again
on the battlefield like this.

38:08.360 --> 38:13.160
Now you have settled
the debt of that injustice.

38:16.400 --> 38:17.800
General, we are under attack.

38:17.880 --> 38:19.240
We have been surrounded.

38:21.440 --> 38:22.600
Is it someone looking for you?

38:23.480 --> 38:24.720
Who wants you dead?

38:26.440 --> 38:28.120
It could be anyone.

38:28.200 --> 38:31.920
To claim the throne,
one must first remove the predecessor.

38:33.200 --> 38:37.440
I want to see
who can actually take my life.

38:37.520 --> 38:39.280
You can butcher each other for all I care,

38:39.880 --> 38:43.000
but you must not die
within the State of Chu.

38:43.600 --> 38:44.560
Follow me.

38:45.080 --> 38:46.160
Hurry.

38:54.120 --> 38:54.960
Go!

39:28.560 --> 39:29.440
Mr. Xie,

39:30.600 --> 39:32.920
I heard that Her Highness
is personally leading another campaign.

39:33.000 --> 39:34.160
Has she developed a taste for war,

39:35.160 --> 39:38.640
or is she acting out of spite
because Xiao Xun declared

39:38.720 --> 39:39.720
he would take her as his Empress?

39:40.320 --> 39:44.280
Regardless of the reason,
if she wants to do it, she should go.

39:44.800 --> 39:46.400
We need only pave the road for her,

39:47.480 --> 39:51.320
just like the dead-end road
we paved for Yanlai.

39:53.040 --> 39:54.240
I received a secret report.

39:57.240 --> 39:58.600
Yanlai is dead.

39:59.280 --> 40:00.760
He died believing

40:01.560 --> 40:03.840
that the ones who attacked him
and the Northern Desert King

40:03.920 --> 40:05.240
were Xiao Xun's men.

40:05.840 --> 40:07.600
You are truly far-sighted.

40:10.360 --> 40:14.840
Deng Yi dying at her hands
is better than him dying at mine.

40:14.920 --> 40:18.680
They started with an alliance
and ended up shattered by infighting.

40:19.680 --> 40:21.880
Once she learns of Yanlai's death,

40:23.240 --> 40:25.440
there will be no reconciliation
between her and Xiao Xun.

40:29.400 --> 40:32.640
Well, are the night refreshments ready?

40:33.560 --> 40:34.400
Yes.

40:34.480 --> 40:37.920
Have them packed
and delivered to Her Highness.

40:38.000 --> 40:42.440
You are far too good to her, Mr. Xie,
yet gratitude is not in her nature.

40:43.120 --> 40:44.360
I don't know what you are aiming for.

40:50.560 --> 40:55.800
The better I treat her now,
the greater her agony will be.

40:57.640 --> 41:02.000
Once she kills Xiao Xun
and returns covered in wounds,

41:03.400 --> 41:05.440
I must ensure she has a place
to return to.

41:12.640 --> 41:15.000
That scoundrel Xiao Xun
actually dared to declare

41:15.080 --> 41:16.520
that he would take
Your Highness as his empress.

41:18.400 --> 41:21.120
All he wants is for me
to become what he is,

41:21.640 --> 41:23.360
a rebel who seized the throne

41:23.920 --> 41:25.840
and deserves to be struck down by all.

41:25.920 --> 41:28.040
Your Highness, you should march
out with the troops now

41:28.120 --> 41:30.280
and claim his head
before the eyes of the world.

41:47.400 --> 41:49.920
Your Highness, are you feeling unwell?

41:50.640 --> 41:51.800
I don't know what is wrong.

41:52.920 --> 41:54.240
I feel terribly anxious.

42:07.600 --> 42:10.800
<i>My chances of winning are higher</i>
<i>in this battle against Xiao Xun.</i>

42:11.320 --> 42:14.560
<i>Even if it is difficult to defy fate,</i>
<i>at worst, we will fight to the death.</i>

42:15.840 --> 42:19.160
<i>Yet why does my heart feel so unsettled?</i>

42:21.800 --> 42:23.400
Your Highness, urgent report
from the frontier.

42:24.000 --> 42:26.440
-What has happened at the frontier?
-It is General Fu Jiu.

42:28.760 --> 42:29.600
What about Jiu?

42:29.680 --> 42:31.560
General Fu Jiu
and the Northern Desert King

42:31.640 --> 42:32.680
were ambushed by an unknown army.

42:33.280 --> 42:34.120
Whether they survived is unclear.

42:50.280 --> 42:52.440
SOARING SPIRIT

42:57.400 --> 42:59.440
-Are you going to the frontier?
-Yes.

43:00.040 --> 43:02.520
-Must you go?
-Yes.

43:03.440 --> 43:04.520
He is dead.

43:15.040 --> 43:18.680
No body means there is still a chance.

43:19.880 --> 43:23.480
I believe General Zhong
has been looking for him.

43:26.520 --> 43:27.800
If you are worried,

43:30.280 --> 43:31.520
I will send more men.

43:33.240 --> 43:36.440
If he is alive,
I will retrieve him myself.

43:37.840 --> 43:38.680
If he is gone,

43:40.280 --> 43:41.960
I will do everything in my power
to uncover the truth.

43:44.240 --> 43:45.800
You are the Grand Princess.

43:46.320 --> 43:48.400
Xiao Xun has risen in revolt,

43:49.240 --> 43:51.320
and you would leave the court
over something so absurd?

43:52.560 --> 43:56.680
If something happens,
you will regret it forever.

43:57.520 --> 44:00.080
Do you think I am doing this
only for one Xie Yanlai?

44:01.480 --> 44:02.920
As the Grand Princess,

44:03.920 --> 44:05.840
if I remain indifferent
to the unjust death

44:07.040 --> 44:08.480
of a loyal general,

44:10.240 --> 44:12.160
who else will be willing
to give their life for the state?

44:36.520 --> 44:39.360
Xie Yanfang, you dare try to kill me?

44:40.320 --> 44:41.520
By leaving the court
without sanction, Your Highness

44:41.600 --> 44:42.720
is putting the very foundation
of the state at risk.

44:42.800 --> 44:45.280
Since I am aware of this,
I cannot ignore it.

44:46.400 --> 44:50.280
If you come back with me,
I will pretend nothing happened.
